---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About" description="What coverit is, our philosophy, and why we built it.">
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 py-16 md:py-24">

    <!-- 1. What is Coverit -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
        What is coverit?
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
        AI made writing code trivially easy. Teams ship faster than ever. But "fast" without
        "safe" is just technical debt accumulating at 10x speed. Coverage numbers don't tell you
        the truth about your codebase &mdash; coverit does.
      </p>
      <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        coverit is an AI-powered test quality platform that gives you a real confidence signal.
        It scans 5 quality dimensions (mapped to ISO 25010), identifies real gaps, generates tests
        to fill them, and tracks your score over time. The test generation is the delivery mechanism &mdash;
        the <span class="text-text font-semibold">confidence signal</span> is the product.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-20">
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
      <span class="block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. Philosophy -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-10">
        Our Philosophy
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-10">
        <!-- Principle 1 -->
        <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6 md:pl-8">
          <p class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">
            "Coverage isn't quality."
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            80% line coverage means nothing if your tests don't catch real bugs.
            coverit measures what matters: functionality, security, stability,
            conformance, and regression.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Principle 2 -->
        <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6 md:pl-8">
          <p class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">
            "The Testing Diamond, not the Pyramid."
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Integration tests at 50%, not unit tests. Real dependencies, real boundaries.
            The balance that actually catches bugs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Principle 3 -->
        <div class="border-l-2 border-accent pl-6 md:pl-8">
          <p class="font-heading text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">
            "AI explores, not heuristics."
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            No pattern matching or static analysis. coverit gives AI real tools &mdash;
            file access, code search, command execution &mdash; and lets it understand
            your codebase like a senior engineer would.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-20">
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
      <span class="block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. The Manifest -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
        coverit.json
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Everything lives in one file. Your quality score, module breakdown, gaps,
        journeys, contracts &mdash; all in coverit.json. It's git-tracked, persistent,
        and the single source of truth.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-bg-code rounded-lg p-5 md:p-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <pre class="font-mono text-sm md:text-base text-[#e6dfd4] leading-relaxed"><code>{`{
  "projectName": "my-api",
  "score": 72,
  "dimensions": {
    "functionality": { "score": 85, "gaps": 3 },
    "security":      { "score": 60, "gaps": 7 },
    "stability":     { "score": 78, "gaps": 4 },
    "conformance":   { "score": 65, "gaps": 5 },
    "regression":    { "score": 70, "gaps": 2 }
  },
  "modules": [ "..." ],
  "journeys": [ "..." ],
  "contracts": [ "..." ]
}`}</code></pre>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-20">
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
      <span class="block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- 4. Open Source -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
        Open Source
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
        coverit is free and open source under the AGPL-3.0 license. We believe test quality
        should be transparent, measurable, and community-driven.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/devness-com/coverit"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 font-body text-lg text-accent hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z" />
          </svg>
          GitHub Repository
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@devness/coverit"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 font-body text-lg text-accent hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z" />
          </svg>
          npm Package
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/devness-com/coverit/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 font-body text-lg text-accent hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4" />
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87" />
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75" />
          </svg>
          Contributing Guide
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-20">
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
      <span class="block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber"></span>
      <span class="block h-px w-16 bg-border"></span>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. Built by Devness -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
        Built by Devness
      </h2>
      <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        coverit is built by
        <a
          href="https://devness.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover transition-colors"
        >Devness</a>
        &mdash; a small team passionate about developer tools and AI-assisted development.
      </p>
    </section>

  </article>
</PageLayout>
